                     <title xml:lang="ar-Latn-x-lc" key="work_7761">Šarḥ Fuṣūl Abuqrāṭ li Ibn al-Quff</title>
                     <title xml:lang="ar" key="work_7761">شرح فصول أبقراط لابن القف الكركي</title>
                     <note>Original manuscript in the University and Research Library of Gotha.</note>
                     <note>This is a lemmatically arranged commentary. The introduction begins on f. 2b; the beginning of each Book is as follows: Bk1: 2b; Bk2: 95b; Bk3: 224b. Bk4-7 are in <ref target="http://www.fihrist.org.uk/profile/manuscript/88d2ad0c-e165-494b-8608-c9cc9f261915">MS 1895</ref>.</note>
